from typing import Iterator
# https://open.canada.ca/data/en/dataset/f3e63186-8401-4c9e-a490-1f9e7d7eb00b
# Occupational Health and Safety worker fatality and critical injury counts report

# Because of the small data size and rough graphs, we did a linear bulkup operation.

injuries = pd.read_csv("https://data.ontario.ca/dataset/f3e63186-8401-4c9e-a490-1f9e7d7eb00b/resource/933f4858-4af9-491d-8ded-1375483bc5e2/download/2019-20_ohs_critical_injuries.csv")

injuries_origin = injuries.copy()
injuries_origin.index = pd.date_range(datetime(int(injuries_origin["Calendar Year"].iloc[0])-1, 1, 1), datetime(int(injuries_origin["Calendar Year"].iloc[-1]), 1, 1), freq="Y")
injuries_origin = injuries_origin[injuries_origin.index <= datetime(2017, 12, 31)].copy()

time = []
total = np.array([])
for index, value in enumerate(injuries["Calendar Year"]):
  if index != (len(injuries)-1):
    start = injuries.loc[index]["Total"]
    end = injuries.loc[index+1]["Total"]

    total = np.append(total, np.linspace(start, end, 13)[:12])
    time += pd.date_range(datetime(value, 1, 1), datetime(value, 12, 31), freq="M")

ranged_injuries = pd.DataFrame({"datetime": time, "Total": total})
ranged_injuries.set_index("datetime", inplace=True)
ranged_injuries = ranged_injuries[ranged_injuries.index < datetime(2018, 1, 1)].copy()

# https://open.canada.ca/data/en/dataset/d6b45dd5-22eb-4b24-b37f-ed22469f093f
# Prevalence of cannabis consumption in Canada

cannabis = pd.read_csv("/content/drive/MyDrive/36100597.csv", index_col=0)
total_cannabis = pd.DataFrame(cannabis.groupby(cannabis.index)["VALUE"].sum())

time = []
total = np.array([])

for index, value in enumerate(total_cannabis.index):
  if index != (len(total_cannabis)-1):
    start = total_cannabis.iloc[index]["VALUE"]
    end = total_cannabis.iloc[index+1]["VALUE"]

    total = np.append(total, np.linspace(start, end, 13)[:12])
    time += pd.date_range(datetime(value, 1, 1), datetime(value, 12, 31), freq="M")

linear_bulk_cannabis = pd.DataFrame({"datetime": time, "Total": total})
linear_bulk_cannabis.set_index("datetime", inplace=True)
ranged_cannabis = linear_bulk_cannabis[linear_bulk_cannabis.index >= datetime(2011, 1, 1)].copy()
ranged_cannabis['Formated_Total'] = ranged_cannabis['Total'].map('{:,.2f}'.format)

cannabis_origin = total_cannabis.copy()
cannabis_origin.index = pd.date_range(datetime(int(total_cannabis.index[0])-1, 1, 1), datetime(int(total_cannabis.index[-1]), 1, 1), freq="Y")
cannabis_origin = cannabis_origin[cannabis_origin.index >= datetime(2010, 1, 1)].copy()
cannabis_origin = cannabis_origin[cannabis_origin.index < datetime(2018, 1, 1)].copy()
cannabis_origin["Total"] = cannabis_origin.VALUE

ranged_cannabis["ac"] = [ranged_cannabis.Total.autocorr(lag=i) for i in range(max_leg)]

In [ ]:
# Define the history
injuries_hist = list(injuries_train.Total_log.dropna().astype(float))

# Initialize container for predictions
injuries_pred = []
for i in range(len(injuries_test)):
    # Initalize the model
    arima = ARIMA(injuries_hist, order=(1,1,1))
    # Fit the model on the available history
    arima_fit = arima.fit(disp=0, maxiter=500)
    # Take the prediction
    injuries_pred.append(arima_fit.forecast()[0][0]) 
    # Expand the history
    injuries_hist.append(injuries_test.Total_log[i])
